00:01:27.253 --> 00:01:28.671
Hey, send me one of those hats.

00:01:28.838 --> 00:01:29.881
Go for Greg Belmont.

00:01:30.048 --> 00:01:31.508
Greg! It's Squarepainter, man!

00:01:31.549 --> 00:01:33.635
I just gotta show you this new awesome piece of new artwork I did.

00:01:33.676 --> 00:01:36.096
It's of your ancestor Simon Belmont!

00:01:36.304 --> 00:01:38.431
That looks good, bro! Send it to the Louvre!

00:01:38.598 --> 00:01:42.435
Tell them to put it next to like Leonardo or Donatello or one of those other two turtles.

00:01:42.602 --> 00:01:45.438
I'm not exactly sure they would take it.

00:01:45.563 --> 00:01:48.233
They'll do it! I'm Greg Belmont! Saved the world!

00:01:48.441 --> 00:01:49.776
Sure thing Mr. Belmont.

00:01:50.527 --> 00:01:51.528
Go for Belmont!

00:01:51.778 --> 00:01:53.863
What? I thought I was skyping with Roo!

00:01:54.114 --> 00:01:56.032
Who are you? How did you get my number?

00:01:56.199 --> 00:01:58.993
Hey, I don't get numbers. Numbers get me, bro!

00:01:59.119 --> 00:02:02.122
You look a little familiar. Weren't you the guy from Shatterhand?

00:02:02.330 --> 00:02:03.957
No wait! You're the Bionic Commando!

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:06.126
