00:02:14.801 --> 00:02:16.136
Hello, Greg.

00:02:16.344 --> 00:02:18.304
Oh hey, it's you.

00:02:19.139 --> 00:02:20.306
Again.

00:02:20.348 --> 00:02:21.891
