00:02:24.102 --> 00:02:27.355
Well, you know. It's kinda of...you were. You were there.

00:02:27.438 --> 00:02:30.441
I see how it is. You must've figured out Deborah's Cliff.

00:02:30.525 --> 00:02:34.112
Resurrected Dracula. Defeated Dracula and done all of that, huh?

00:02:34.362 --> 00:02:35.071
Did you?

00:02:35.321 --> 00:02:36.281
DID YOU!?

00:02:36.489 --> 00:02:39.242
I mean, I'm getting to it. Eventually.

00:02:39.325 --> 00:02:41.286
That girl is so mean to him.

00:02:41.327 --> 00:02:43.997
Yeah, Greg's so gorgeous.

00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:47.333
Damnit, Belmont. There is a great evil coming upon this land.

00:02:47.417 --> 00:02:49.335
A greater evil than you would ever know!

00:02:49.377 --> 00:02:54.257
