00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:55.550
We love you, Greg Belmont!

00:02:55.592 --> 00:02:56.885
I wanna have your baby!

00:02:56.968 --> 00:02:58.178
Groupies, please.

00:02:58.344 --> 00:02:59.179
Firstly...

00:02:59.470 --> 00:03:00.722
Margaritas!

00:03:00.805 --> 00:03:03.975
Okay and B: Why are you screaming at me?

00:03:04.434 --> 00:03:05.810
I should be the one!

00:03:06.394 --> 00:03:07.520
Flip it around.

00:03:07.562 --> 00:03:08.646
And switch it and then...

00:03:08.688 --> 00:03:10.023
I'm you... I yell at you!

00:03:10.148 --> 00:03:11.566
I'm sending an ally to you.

00:03:11.608 --> 00:03:14.277
Try not acting like a complete ass to him, too.

00:03:14.402 --> 00:03:16.070
Yeah. You know it. Yeah.

00:03:16.112 --> 00:03:17.947
Wait, wait, wait! There's more! There's more I have to tell you!

00:03:17.989 --> 00:03:18.990
There's not more.

00:03:20.033 --> 00:03:21.701
Bronson, disable wifi please.

00:03:21.784 --> 00:03:23.995
Whatever you wish, sir. Yes.

00:03:24.245 --> 00:03:27.707
As usual, she was cryptic and a complete waste of my time!

00:03:27.832 --> 00:03:30.043
Like, I vanquished the evil that lurks!

00:03:30.210 --> 00:03:33.463
I don't need her. Ah, the world's gonna end!

00:03:33.630 --> 00:03:36.007
Blah, blah, blah, blah. Boyfriend!

00:03:36.090 --> 00:03:37.759
Blah, blah, blah.

00:03:37.926 --> 00:03:39.552
*Annoyed grunting*

00:03:39.928 --> 00:03:42.597
So I'm hunting him. He ducks behind a tree thinking he got away.

00:03:42.764 --> 00:03:44.599
I jump out and decry stop foul being!

00:03:45.391 --> 00:03:46.517
So scared he almost peed.

00:03:52.440 --> 00:03:54.901
