00:03:54.984 --> 00:03:57.737
Bronson, why are you letting cosplay chicks in my luau?

00:03:57.862 --> 00:04:00.198
I, Alucard, son of Dracula

00:04:00.281 --> 00:04:02.867
have come to seek out the descendant of Simon Belmont.

00:04:02.951 --> 00:04:03.910
Dracula had a kid?

00:04:03.952 --> 00:04:05.620
Indeed and it is I.

00:04:05.703 --> 00:04:10.458
So Dracula, the most evil vampire ever who my ancestors have defeated countless times

00:04:10.541 --> 00:04:14.754
Got his undead on with some chick, your mom, producing you.

00:04:14.837 --> 00:04:17.423
Yeah, you are correct, young Belmont.

00:04:17.507 --> 00:04:19.050
Let me recap. Let's wind it back!

00:04:19.175 --> 00:04:21.261
You! Your dad is Dracula!

00:04:21.552 --> 00:04:25.807
Who's been killed hundreds of times. He's dead. Nothing in his self works

00:04:25.932 --> 00:04:29.852
and he got enough baby juice in his balls to produce you.

00:04:29.978 --> 00:04:32.605
