00:04:32.730 --> 00:04:35.358
You're out in daylight and you're not sparkling? What's up?

00:04:35.483 --> 00:04:39.070
As a dhamphir, my human side makes me immune to the effects of sunlight. 

00:04:39.279 --> 00:04:40.738
That sounds really dirty.

00:04:40.822 --> 00:04:42.824
