00:04:47.078 --> 00:04:50.415
I am not here to fight you, young Belmont. I'm here to form an alliance with you.

00:04:50.456 --> 00:04:56.045
You see, many centuries ago, I assisted in the defeat of my father with your ancestor Trevor Belmont.

00:04:56.129 --> 00:04:59.799
Uncle Trevor! I heard he got all kinds of ass. Huh.

00:04:59.966 --> 00:05:01.050
