00:05:01.134 --> 00:05:03.761
After feeling the guilt of defeating my father

00:05:03.803 --> 00:05:07.307
As well as the pity I have on the human race in tribute to my mother Lisa.

00:05:07.432 --> 00:05:10.601
I went into a deep sleep only to be awoken when a new evil emerges.

00:05:10.727 --> 00:05:14.856
I destroyed al the emo vampires. Did nobody read my book?

00:05:14.939 --> 00:05:17.608
But out of the shadows, a new form of vampire will emerge.

00:05:17.734 --> 00:05:22.780
You see, Dracula's army will reign upon this world until they are vanquished by the morning sun. 

00:05:23.114 --> 00:05:24.115
